snippet.title: Yupitergrad 2 - The Lost Station | Full Game Walkthrough | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Yupitergrad 2: The Lost Station is a stand-alone sequel to the highly acclaimed Yupitergrad, known for its satisfying movement system and twisted, Slavic humor. Sounds good? Well, here is part 2! And you don't even have to know Yupitergrad 1 to enjoy the sequel.

SUBSCRIBE - https://www.youtube.com/c/99THVR

PC Specs
- RTX 3070
- Ryzen 7 5800x CPU
- 32 GB DDR4 3600mhz RAM

#99thVR #VirtualReality #yupitergrad2
